  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The CHICA system is a clinical decision support system that uses adaptive turnaround
      documents to provide point-of-care information to clinicians. The investigators will be
      studying whether it can help in the diagnosis and treatment of tuberculosis and iron
      deficiency anemia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The CHICA system is a clinical decision support system that uses adaptive turnaround
      documents to provide point-of-care information to clinicians. We will be studying whether it
      can help in the diagnosis and treatment of tuberculosis and iron deficiency anemia.
    </textblock>
